OL,3,CMan charged with murder following a
OL,4,Cshooting in Nottingham
OL,6,FA man has been charged on suspicion of
OL,7,Fmurder by police after another man was
OL,8,Fkilled by a fatal shooting in
OL,9,FNottingham on Saturday (February 28).
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,12,Fproperty in Ryeland Gardens, The
OL,13,FMeadows, Nottingham, shortly after
OL,14,F5:30am last weekend.
OL,16,FCoel Tainton, 24, sustained a fatal
OL,17,Fgunshot wound and was treated at the
OL,18,Fscene but died a short time later.
