OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1772615079
OL,3,CMan charged with murder following a
OL,4,Cshooting in Nottingham
OL,6,FJack Preston, 34, was arrested on
OL,7,FSaturday and has been subsequently
OL,8,Fcharged on suspicion of murder,
OL,9,Fassault by beating of an emergency
OL,10,Fworker and a public order offence
OL,11,Ftonight (Tuesday 3 March).
OL,13,FPreston, 34, remains in custody and is
OL,14,Fdue to appear at Nottingham
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court tomorrow (4 March).
OL,17,FDetective Inspector Clare Gibson,
OL,18,Fsenior investigating officer, said:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
