PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1772615079
OL,3,CMan charged with murder following a
OL,4,Cshooting in Nottingham
OL,6,F"As we announce these charges today,
OL,7,Four thoughts firmly remain with Coel's
OL,8,Ffamily and friends.
OL,10,F"Specially trained officers are
OL,11,Fproviding them with support, and this
OL,12,Fwill continue.
OL,14,F"Our team of investigators and
OL,15,Fspecialist officers have worked
OL,16,Fextremely hard over the past few days
OL,17,Fto determine the full circumstances of
OL,18,Fwhat happened, and I am pleased we
OL,19,Fhave now been able to charge a suspect
OL,20,Fin this case."
